.Sh NAME
.Nm mtio
.Nd
.Tn UNIX
magtape interface
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The special files
named
.Pa /dev/mt0
and
.Pa /dev/rmt0
through
.Pa /dev/mt23
and
.Pa /dev/rmt23
refer to
.Tn UNIX
magtape drives,
which may be on the
.Tn MASSBUS
using the
.Tn TM03
formatter
.Xr ht 4 ,
or
.Tn TM78
formatter,
.Xr mt 4 ,
or on the
.Tn UNIBUS
using either the
.Tn TM11
or
.Tn TS11
formatters
.Xr tm 4 ,
.Tn TU45
compatible formatters,
.Xr ut 4 ,
or
.Xr ts 4 .
These devices are typical tape block devices,
see
.Xr physio 4 .
.Pp
